edu.ucla.sspace.vector
Class ScaledSparseDoubleVector

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.vector.ScaledDoubleVector
      edu.ucla.sspace.vector.ScaledSparseDoubleVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
DoubleVector, SparseDoubleVector, SparseVector<Double>, Vector<Double>
public class ScaledSparseDoubleVector
extends ScaledDoubleVector
implements SparseDoubleVector

A decorator for SparseDoubleVectors that scales every value in a given DoubleVector by some non zero scale.

Note that this automatically computes the scaling of a ScaledDoubleVector so that backing vector is scaled only once, thus preventing any recursive calls to scaling.

Author:
Keith Stevens
